@EXPORTS
layout.tsx: AdminLayout — admin section layout with sidebar navigation & admin check
page.tsx: AdminDashboardPage — admin overview with stats
achievements/page.tsx: AdminAchievementsPage — CRUD for achievements/badges
chapters/page.tsx: AdminChaptersPage — manage chapters & their questions
users/page.tsx: AdminUsersPage — user management (list, edit, toggle admin)
analytics/page.tsx: AdminAnalyticsPage — platform usage analytics & charts
hackathons/page.tsx: AdminHackathonsPage — list hackathons
hackathons/new/page.tsx: NewHackathonPage — create hackathon form
hackathons/[id]/page.tsx: HackathonDetailPage — view hackathon details
hackathons/[id]/edit/page.tsx: EditHackathonPage — edit hackathon form
hackathons/components/hackathon-form.tsx: HackathonForm — reusable hackathon form component

@PROCESSES
AdminAccess: check isAdmin flag on user → redirect to / if not admin
HackathonCRUD: list → create/edit form → POST/PUT /api/admin/hackathons → manage teams & projects

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: @/lib/admin-auth, @/components/ui, @/lib/validation-schemas
external: next-auth/react, react, next/navigation

@STANDARDS
- All admin pages require isAdmin flag
- AdminLayout wraps all admin pages with sidebar nav
- Hackathon form is shared between create and edit pages
